        "evidence": "<p>Addition of the assigned points; if there has been limb ischemia for more than 6 hours, the \"limb ischemia\" points are doubled.</p>",
        "facts": "<div class=\"table-responsive\">\n<table class=\"table table-bordered\" style=\"width: 100.121%; height: 537.562px;\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 22.3984px;\">\n<th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align: left; width: 73.1884%; height: 22.3984px;\">Variable</th>\n<th style=\"text-align: left; width: 26.8116%; height: 22.3984px;\">Points</th>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 44.7969px;\">\n<td rowspan=\"3\" style=\"width: 21.5075%; height: 134.391px;\">Limb ischemia*</td>\n<td style=\"width: 51.6809%; height: 44.7969px;\">Reduced pulse but normal perfusion</td>\n<td style=\"width: 26.8116%; height: 44.7969px;\">1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 44.7969px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 51.6809%; height: 44.7969px;\">Pulseless, paresthesias, slow capillary refill</td>\n<td style=\"width: 26.8116%; height: 44.7969px;\">2</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 44.7969px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 51.6809%; height: 44.7969px;\">Cool, paralysis, numb/insensate</td>\n<td style=\"width: 26.8116%; height: 44.7969px;\">3</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 22.3984px;\">\n<td rowspan=\"3\" style=\"width: 21.5075%; height: 67.1952px;\">Patient age range</td>\n<td style=\"width: 51.6809%; height: 22.3984px;\">&lt;30</td>\n<td style=\"width: 26.8116%; height: 22.3984px;\">0</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 22.3984px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 51.6809%; height: 22.3984px;\">30-50</td>\n<td style=\"width: 26.8116%; height: 22.3984px;\">1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 22.3984px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 51.6809%; height: 22.3984px;\">&ge;50</td>\n<td style=\"width: 26.8116%; height: 22.3984px;\">2</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 44.7969px;\">\n<td rowspan=\"3\" style=\"width: 21.5075%; height: 89.5937px;\">Shock</td>\n<td style=\"width: 51.6809%; height: 44.7969px;\"><abbr title=\"Systolic Blood Pressure\">SBP</abbr> &gt;90 mmHg consistently</td>\n<td style=\"width: 26.8116%; height: 44.7969px;\">0</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 22.3984px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 51.6809%; height: 22.3984px;\">Hypotension transiently</td>\n<td style=\"width: 26.8116%; height: 22.3984px;\">1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 22.3984px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 51.6809%; height: 22.3984px;\">Persistent hypotension</td>\n<td style=\"width: 26.8116%; height: 22.3984px;\">2</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 44.7969px;\">\n<td rowspan=\"4\" style=\"width: 21.5075%; height: 223.984px;\">Injury&nbsp; mechanism</td>\n<td style=\"width: 51.6809%; height: 44.7969px;\">Low energy (stab, gunshot, simple fracture)</td>\n<td style=\"width: 26.8116%; height: 44.7969px;\">1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 67.1953px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 51.6809%; height: 67.1953px;\">Medium energy (dislocation, open/multiple fractures)</td>\n<td style=\"width: 26.8116%; height: 67.1953px;\">2</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 44.7969px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 51.6809%; height: 44.7969px;\">High energy (high speed MVA or rifle shot)</td>\n<td style=\"width: 26.8116%; height: 44.7969px;\">3</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 67.1953px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 51.6809%; height: 67.1953px;\">Very high energy (high speed trauma with gross contamination)</td>\n<td style=\"width: 26.8116%; height: 67.1953px;\">4</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>*If Limb ischemia present &gt;6 hours, Limb ischemia points are multiplied by 2.</p>\n</div>",
